# Demo: list pipelines (fleets)
Output assets/edx-pipelines.gif
Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 15
Set Width 1200
Set Height 480
Set Padding 12
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 25ms

Type "edx pipelines list --output table --columns tag,fleet_type,environment,status | head -12"
Sleep 600ms
Enter
Sleep 4.5s
